§0
§0Welcome to the§0
§0second Government§0
§0Gazette of my term§0
§0as Mayor. As before,§0
§0I'll try to keep§0
§0it brief.
#- §lCupboard§0
§0
§0After elections with§0
§0a dearth of eligible§0
§0candidates, I have§0
§0appointed waffle4-§0
§0breakfast Cup for§0
§0Infrastructure. I§0
§0have also appointed§0
§0squareblob as Cup§0
§0for Culture. This§0
§0is in addition to
#- the existing cup-§0
§0board.
#- §lJudge election§0
§0
§0You can now announce§0
§0your campaign for§0
§0Judge if you are eli-§0
§0gible; this is the§0
§0position I vacated§0
§0upon being elected§0
§0Mayor.
#- §lOlympics§0
§0
§0The Olympics are§0
§0coming to Mount§0
§0Augusta in August!§0
§0Serious and in-depth§0
§0preparations are§0
§0beginning, enquire§0
§0within if you would§0
§0like to help, else§0
§0watch this space.
#- §lCitizenship reform§0
§0
§0The first major re-§0
§0form I have attempted§0
§0as Mayor is now under§0
§0vote. I intend to§0
§0continue to propose§0
§0major law reforms§0
§0every couple of weeks§0
§0from this time onwards,§0
§0in much the same way§0
§0as I have conducted
#- this one. Feel free§0
§0to speak to me about§0
§0any concerns in the§0
§0process or contents.
#- §lEmbassy in Icenia§0
§0
§0Dr_Oracle has begun§0
§0building the embassy§0
§0of Mount Augusta in§0
§0Icenia. He wants me§0
§0to say that he is on§0
§0his last warning; I§0
§0don't know, it's some§0
§0kind of weird roleplay§0
§0thing I guess.
#- §l     ----+----§0
§0
§0Before I finish this§0
§0Gazette, I want to§0
§0clarify its nature a§0
§0little as I did not§0
§0last week; it is in-§0
§0tended to keep people§0
§0up to date with the§0
§0activities of spe-§0
§0cifically the admini-§0
§0stration, which is
#- to say the Mayor,§0
§0the Cupboard (in-§0
§0cluding the Diplomat)§0
§0and such. It is not§0
§0a legally binding§0
§0document, nor is it§0
§0involved with the§0
§0affairs of the ju-§0
§0dicial system of§0
§0Mount Augusta, which§0
§0operates on§0
§0r/mtaugustajustice.
#- Alright; until next time.§0
